499
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] A nema odgovora na ta pitanja.

500
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi ljudi to uviđaju.

501
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:30,000
